 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003ESmartify turns customer data into actionable insights - not by tracking every metric, but by tracking the right metrics. Our platform takes demographic \u0026amp; psychographic data from your customers\u0026#8217; social media profiles and helps you apply them for efficient use in your marketing \u0026amp; sales efforts. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThe Smartify customer intimacy platform allows brands and retailers to recognize and reward customers with personalized content and discounts in real-time, getting them to buy more and share their affinity with friends. Promotional features incentivize users to share your promotion with friends, sign up for email communications, and engage with you through social, mobile, and in-person channels. When integrated seamlessly throughout your website, the Smartify platform takes rewards to the next level, delivering personalized messages and discounts to customers, increasing sales and driving more efficient loyalty-driven acquisition. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EWhen consumers opt in to your branded Smartify program, the social media profile data collected helps you understand your customers\u2019 brand preferences, and gives you the opportunity to connect with them via their preferred channels. Smartify is the only platform that deploys seamlessly across all marketing channels: websites, email, direct mail, e-commerce sites, mobile, social platforms, point of sale, and more. Smartify\u2019s analytics provides the insight needed to launch a true multi-channel customer acquisition effort.\u003C/p\u003E",
